metadata.name: On Shelter
metadata.description:
"You shouldn't be here, they usually shout a signal when I'm around," Leopard said. Secret bride answered, "In the mysterious wilderness everything seems clear, who is the hunter and who is being hunted. Camouflage belongs only to small predators. Whereas in what seems a human place, everything seems vague. The more camouflage the more the prey and getting to the top. Besides, the sun looks more beautiful and natural here."
After which both of them were immersed in the light.
